    "description": "Every star dies...<br><br>In this roguelike action game, you are the sole survivor of a dead planet. Battle alien hordes as you fight to outlast a dying universe. Gather resources and build a synergistic collection of upgrades and followers to help you avenge your home world and obliterate anything that stands in your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight!</h2><br>Gather an arsenal of weapons and followers to battle a never-ending host of alien oddities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694740/extras/0cdb72b9c8a550a455a83d7688aa7aa0.poster.avif?t=1713050237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694740/extras/0cdb72b9c8a550a455a83d7688aa7aa0.webm?t=1713050237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1694740/extras/0cdb72b9c8a550a455a83d7688aa7aa0.mp4?t=1713050237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scavenge!</h2><br>Scour each Solar System to find the richest mineral deposits, and use your army of probes to collect them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade!</h2><br>Use the minerals you've gathered to enhance your ship. With each run offering a different series of upgrade choices, your best resource will be your ever-expanding knowledge of the opportunities and challenges waiting in the next system.",
